					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">NES:<br />My parents bought it for me, reasoning that they overcharged for the 'super' prefix to the SNES. With it i got Castlevania 3, which is still my favourite game i can play any day there's time. I also got barker bill's trick shooting, which i haven't played in 17 years, i think. <br /><br />Between here and the next console phase, i was all Mac shareware scene and then PC. <br />Console games were played, but over at friends. <br /><br />Wii:<br />Metroid Prime trilogy - i had built up some anticipation for the first two titles but never took the plunge for a game cube. When this got released, i bought a Wii for just for the sake of playing these. <br /><br />Wii U:<br />Mario kart 8 and Splatoon.</div>

					
